<chapter xml:id="ch-chapter-title" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>The Fundamentals of Differential Equations</title>

  <introduction>
    <p> In this chapter we introduce the idea of a differential equation, learn some important techniques for solving them
  separable ODEs and 1st order linear ODEs, and see a few common applications of differential equations. 
    </p>
  </introduction>

